R6 Class for large Tensor (Array) in Hybrid Mode

Tensor.Rd

can store on hard drive, and read slices of GB-level data in seconds

Public fields

dim

dimension of the array

dimnames

dimension names of the array

use_index

whether to use one dimension as index when storing data as multiple files

swap_file

file or files to save data to

hybrid

whether to allow data to be written to disk

last_used

timestamp of the object was read

temporary

whether to remove the files once garbage collected

Active bindings

varnames

dimension names (read-only)

read_only

whether to protect the swap files from being changed

Arguments

numeric array

varnames

characters, names of dimnames

hybrid

whether to enable hybrid mode

use_index

whether to use the last dimension for indexing

swap_file

where to store the data in hybrid mode files to save data by index

temporary

whether to remove temporary files when existing

multi_files

Method to_swap()

Serialize tensor to a file and store it via write_fst

Usage

Tensor$to_swap(use_index = FALSE, delay = 0)

Arguments

use_index

whether to use one of the dimension as index for faster loading

delay

if greater than 0, then check when last used, if not long ago, then do not swap to hard drive. If the difference of time is greater than delay in seconds, then swap immediately.

Method to_swap_now()

Serialize tensor to a file and store it via write_fst immediately

Usage

Tensor$to_swap_now(use_index = FALSE)

Arguments

use_index

whether to use one of the dimension as index for faster loading

Method set_data()

set/replace data with given array

Usage

Tensor$set_data(v)

Arguments

v

the value to replace the old one, must have the same dimension

notice

the a tensor is an environment. If you change at one place, the data from all other places will change. So use it carefully.

Examples


# Create a tensor
ts <- Tensor$new(
  data = 1:18000000, c(3000,300,20),
  dimnames = list(A = 1:3000, B = 1:300, C = 1:20),
  varnames = c('A', 'B', 'C'))

# Size of tensor when in memory is usually large
pryr::object_size(ts)
#> 72.3 MB
#> 8.02 MB

# Enable hybrid mode
ts$to_swap_now()
#> Writing to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e6824ad0d

# Hybrid mode, usually less than 1 MB
pryr::object_size(ts)
#> 282 kB
#> 814 kB

# Subset data
start1 <- Sys.time()
subset(ts, C ~ C < 10 & C > 5, A ~ A < 10)
#> Dimension:  9 x 300 x 4 
#> - A: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6,...
#> - B: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6,...
#> - C: 6, 7, 8, 9
#> Dimension:  9 x 300 x 4 
#> - A: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6,...
#> - B: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6,...
#> - C: 6, 7, 8, 9
end1 <- Sys.time(); end1 - start1
#> Time difference of 0.3443501 secs
#> Time difference of 0.188035 secs

# Join tensors
ts <- lapply(1:20, function(ii){
  Tensor$new(
    data = 1:9000, c(30,300,1),
    dimnames = list(A = 1:30, B = 1:300, C = ii),
    varnames = c('A', 'B', 'C'), use_index = 2)
})
ts <- join_tensors(ts, temporary = TRUE)
#> Writing to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e19ce8000Writing to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e44358d3cWriting to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e17cb8120Writing to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e318a6814Writing to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e75b71274Writing to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e461cba0cWriting to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e7fa8dcaWriting to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e5272ccddWriting to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e6ee7eb74Writing to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e3c13458eWriting to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e153b8c72Writing to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e78819b41Writing to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e4f80636Writing to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e375fc5c6Writing to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e70b16690Writing to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55eec4b1bdWriting to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e1370f6deWriting to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e5d5f72caWriting to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e25695baaWriting to path:  /var/folders/rh/4bkfl5z50wgbbjd85xvc695c0000gn/T//RtmpFMhZU7/filed55e28010916
